## Summary
This documentation explains how to build, analyze, and utilize predictions in Amplitude Activation to segment users based on their likelihood to perform future actions. It covers creating predictive models, analyzing their performance through feature importance and model metrics, and converting predictions into actionable cohorts for targeting and analysis.

